<figureCitation box="[159,245,260,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 14" captionStartId="16.[151,250,1889,1911]" captionTargetBox="[218,1360,194,1867]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1867]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 14. Amphidraus simplex sp. nov. A left male palp, prolateral view; B same, dorsal view; C same, ventral view; D same, retrolateral view; E epigyne, ventral view; F same, cleared, ventral view. CC, cymbial conductor; CO, copulatory opening; dPED, distal process on embolic disc; E, embolus; ED, embolic disc; FD, fertilization duct; po, coupling pocket; PS, primary spermatHeca; RvTA, retroventral tibial apopHysis; SD, sperm duct; SS, secondary spermatHeca; TL, tegular lobe; vPED, ventral process on embolic disc." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/855479/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="418">Figs 14</figureCitation>
