<figureCitation box="[772,857,404,429]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1976,1998]" captionTargetBox="[228,1362,876,1958]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[228,1362,876,1958]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 13. Amphidraus simplex sp. nov. A male Holotype, dorsal view; B same, ventral view; C female paratype, dorsal view; D same, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/855475/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="418">Figs 13</figureCitation>
A, 13B).
</paragraph>
